{"tid":1551430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國國歌香港版】《榮耀永歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-08T04:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T06:12:50.000Z","uid":264429,"like":8,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2316e242db877e02902b6215499124c56f9492da","tid":1551430,"uid":264429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:06:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於好多人話美國國歌melody好難記，又或者唔識啲英文，所以寫左首香港版，唔係直譯，但精神一樣。如果有人幫手唱就好嚕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>《榮耀永歸香港》（調寄：美國國歌》</strong><br />\n<br />\n以長夜為證<br />\n香港必能獲勝<br />\n如同星光永在<br />\n時代主宰的革命<br />\n<br />\n靠著黎明晨曦<br />\n星火中尋路徑<br />\n毋忘犧牲壯士<br />\n迷霧中雙眼漸明<br />\n<br />\n未懼毒氣攻堅<br />\n血肉凌厲奮戰<br />\n呼聲響徹夜<br />\n旗下精神未變<br />\n<br />\n憑意志與力量<br />\n歷劫終可靠岸<br />\n危城下護我邦<br />\n榮耀永歸香港"},{"pid":"c8ca1500355da5ab48e85e7aa7a6725561ba3fee","tid":1551430,"uid":198297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:12:44.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a81e6c4cfad3d0990ab757c91faf1c0ab75f4b","tid":1551430,"uid":266654,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"改人地國歌會唔會唔係咁好?"},{"pid":"cf0039cc880308e7c9837e2b79507da61b620773","tid":1551430,"uid":53368,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:15:57.000Z","msg":"做乜9改人國歌？"},{"pid":"18e2373b0de7863aafa26e118a487677221407cb","tid":1551430,"uid":109780,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T04:17:25.000Z","msg":"改人國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/